| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-6773 — Recovery Inhibition (anubis)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: d66c2321-2c25-502d-9e75-7354e95eeae3"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
